title: CTC ERROR: Saw a non-null label (index >= num_classes - 1) following a null label, batch: 0 num_classes: 12 labels: 2,10,5,1
body_html:
I use TF rc 0.10 to run a project (https://github.com/synckey/tensorflow_lstm_ctc_ocr), but the program raise a error:
Invalid argument: Saw a non-null label (index >= num_classes - 1) following a null label, batch: 0 num_classes: 12 labels: 2,10,5,1

what does it mean?
